<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Brooke Lee | Look Who It Is Podcast</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Brooke Lee joins the Look Who It Is podcast with Dane Engle. Watch and listen to the full episode." />

  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#0b0f14;
      --card:#131a22;
      --card2:#0f141b;
      --text:#f5f7fa;
      --muted:#a7b0bc;
      --line:rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      --accent:#12b76a;
      --accent2:#0ea85f;
      --shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
      --radius:18px;
      --max:1000px;
    }

    *{ box-sizing:border-box; }

    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      color:var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 20% -10%, rgba(18,183,106,.18), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at 100% 0%, rgba(18,183,106,.10), transparent 55%),
        var(--bg);
      padding:24px;
    }

    .wrap{
      max-width:var(--max);
      margin:0 auto;
    }

    .brand{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      font-size:13px;
      color:var(--muted);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);
      padding:8px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      margin-bottom:20px;
    }

    .dot{
      width:8px;
      height:8px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:var(--accent);
      box-shadow:0 0 0 6px rgba(18,183,106,.15);
    }

    .hero{
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, var(--card), var(--card2));
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      padding:36px;
      margin-bottom:24px;
    }

    h1{
      margin:0 0 10px 0;
      font-size:clamp(32px, 5vw, 46px);
      letter-spacing:-0.02em;
    }

    .subtitle{
      font-size:18px;
      color:var(--accent);
      font-weight:600;
      margin-bottom:16px;
    }

    .desc{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.6;
      max-width:700px;
      margin-bottom:24px;
    }

    .buttons{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:12px;
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      padding:14px 20px;
      border-radius:12px;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-weight:600;
      font-size:15px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);
      color:var(--text);
      transition:.12s;
    }

    .btn:hover{
      transform:translateY(-1px);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    }

    .btn.primary{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      color:white;
      border:none;
      box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(18,183,106,.30);
    }

    .btn.primary:hover{
      box-shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(18,183,106,.35);
    }

    .section{
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, var(--card), var(--card2));
      padding:28px;
      margin-bottom:24px;
    }

    .section h2{
      margin:0 0 14px 0;
      font-size:22px;
    }

    .platform-links{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
    }

    .platform{
      padding:10px 14px;
      border-radius:10px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);
      text-decoration:none;
      color:var(--text);
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .platform:hover{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    }

    .footer{
      text-align:center;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:13px;
      margin-top:30px;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="wrap">

  <div class="brand">
    <span class="dot"></span>
    Look Who It Is Podcast • Windrow Studio
  </div>

  <div class="hero">

    <h1>Brooke Lee</h1>

    <div class="subtitle">
      Look Who It Is Podcast Guest
    </div>

    <div class="desc">
      Brooke Lee joins Dane Engle on the Look Who It Is podcast to talk about her path as an artist, the reality of building a career in Nashville, and what it takes to stay in it long term. This episode focuses on process, persistence, and the real work behind the music.
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">

      <!-- Replace these when ready -->
      <a class="btn primary" href="#" target="_blank">
        Watch Full Episode
      </a>

      <a class="btn" href="#" target="_blank">
        Listen on Spotify
      </a>

      <a class="btn" href="https://www.windrowstudio.com/lookwhoitis" target="_blank">
        View All Episodes
      </a>

    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="section">

    <h2>Follow Brooke Lee</h2>

    <div class="platform-links">

      <!-- Replace with her real links -->
      <a class="platform" href="https://www.instagram.com/brookeleemusic/" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
      <a class="platform" href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/7mDMlZnQ1SQRtujvd3azxS?si=FvPoHWzRSISAEsmBhUdDiQ" target="_blank">Spotify</a>
      <a class="platform" href="https://brookeleemusic.com/" target="_blank">Website</a>
      <a class="platform" href="https://www.youtube.com/@brookeleemusic" target="_blank">YouTube</a>

    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="section">

    <h2>About Look Who It Is</h2>

    <div class="desc">
      Look Who It Is is a podcast documenting how musicians actually build and sustain careers. Hosted by Dane Engle, the show focuses on honest conversations with artists, producers, and songwriters working in today's music industry.
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">
      <a class="btn" href="https://www.windrowstudio.com" target="_blank">
        Windrow Studio
      </a>

      <a class="btn" href="https://www.windrowstudio.com/radio" target="_blank">
        Listen to Look Who It Is Radio
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    © Windrow Studio • Look Who It Is Podcast
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
